We released a new version of "BringTheFood":http://www.bringfood.org after a long trial period with "Banco Alimentare":http://www.bancoalimentare.it (the Italian Food Bank).

The biggest change is that private citizens can now use the app like a social network to share food and help charities, with the help of Banco Alimentare who will monitor the network and the quality of donations.

